data.title: Oppenheimer
data.msg: The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.

data.title: The Creator
data.msg: Amid a future war between the human race and the forces of artificial intelligence, a hardened ex-special forces agent grieving the disappearance of his wife, is recruited to hunt down and kill the Creator, the elusive architect of advanced AI who has developed a mysterious weapon with the power to end the war‚Äîand mankind itself.

data.title: Five Nights at Freddy's
data.msg: Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy's is what it seems.

data.title: The Killer
data.msg: After a fateful near-miss, an assassin battles his employers, and himself, on an international manhunt he insists isn't personal.
